About Grove Soho
EXOTIC. ELEVATED. APPROACHABLE.
We are a Tiki-Inspired Tropical Concept focused on providing the community with an elevated alternative to the rest of South Tampa. Our daytime programming included LIVE MUSIC, EXOTIC CUISINE, AND FUN LOVING SERVICE! For the nightlife, we take craft to another level mixing in DJs spinning the jams, cocktails with lights and smoke, and a dance floor to shake things up! Food is always available so long as doors are open. If you do not see a drink on the menu that you like, ask our talented bar staff and they will make your dreams come true.
